Game of Thrones episodes

Source: R/data.R
gameofthrones.Rd

This data comes from https://trakt.tv and https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_House_episodes.

gameofthrones

Format

A tibble with 60 rows and 21 variables:

episode_abs

Overall episode number

episode, season

Episode within each season and season number

epid

Episode ID in s00e00 format

runtime

Runtime in minutes

title

Episode title

year

Year of first airing

overview

Episode summary

rating_

Rating (1-10) on IMDb and trakt.tv

votes

Number of votes and trakt.tv

viewers

Number of viewers (US) in millions

director, writer

Direction and writing credits

first_aired, first_aired.string

Original airdate in UTC as POSIXct and character

trakt, tvdb, tmdb

Episode IDs for trakt.tv, TVDb, and TMDb

See also

Other Episode datasets: futurama
